About SSLproxy
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Welcome
=======
    SSLproxy is a opensource SSL proxy server software for UltraMonkey-L7.

System requirements
===================

           OS : Linux 2.6.9(or later)on x86 and x86_64 architecture
                We recommend to use Redhat Enterprise Linux.

          CPU : Intel x86 and x86_64 or compatible architecture processors

       Memory : 2 GB(recommended)

    Libraries : openssl(0.9.8b or higher), boost(1.36.0 or higher),
                perl, apache log4cxx(0.10 or higher)

License
=======

    SSLproxy is distributed using LGPL License.


About UltraMonkey-L7 Project
============================

    To get more information about SSLproxy, please visit our 
    UltraMonkey-L7 project Web Site.

         Project Web Site - http://ultramonkey-l7.sourceforge.jp/
